             was a second time indicted for <rs id="t17880227-50-off250" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880227-50-off250" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880227-50-off250" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17880227-50-cd251" type="crimeDate">5th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880227-50-off250 t17880227-50-cd251"></join>, an iron axe with a wooden handle, value 1 s. two hand-saws, value 3 s. a key-hole saw, value 3 d. and two brad-awls, value 2 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17880227-50-victim584" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Thomas
