                  , and a wire lime-sieve, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880227-50-victim586" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Anderson
                  <interp inst="t17880227-50-victim586" type="surname" value="Anderson"></interp>
